title: High_Resolution_Non-Nude_Scans
description:
High Resolution Non-Nude Scans:

Images scanned from magazines at high resolution to include the original half-tone colour rendering. Because the half-tone rendering is intact, these images are suitable for printing to any size including life-size and wall-size posters. Image resolution may need to be reduced for accurate
reproduction at small scale to avoid moire interference.
